videoSnippet.title: Amazing Final position in the Famous Planinc Miniature
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator If you enjoy the video, hit that LIKE button :)

The game presented is probably his most famous and you can find the final position in many tactics books.

Rafael Vaganian vs Albin Planinc
"Careful Planinc" (game of the day Dec-26-2008)
Hastings 7475 (1975), Hastings ENG, rd 5, Jan-02 
English Opening: Symmetrical. Anti-Benoni Variation Spielmann Defense (A32)


1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 c5 3. Nf3 cd4 4. Nd4 e6 5. Nc3 Bb4 6. Ndb5 O-O 7. a3 Bc3 8. Nc3 d5 9. Bg5 h6 10. Bf6 Qf6 11. cd5 ed5 12. Qd5 Rd8 13. Qf3 Qb6 14. Rd1 Rd1 15. Nd1 Nc6 16. Qe3 Nd4 17. Qe8 Kh7 18. e3 Nc2 19. Kd2 Bf5 20. Qa8 Qd6 21. Kc1 Na1 22. Qb7 Qc7
